                                                                                                                                    <PT-06(02)_ODP frequency> to ensure that they remain appropriate and necessary
                                                                                                                                    in accordance with law;

                                                                                                              PT-06(02)[02]         all Privacy Act exempons claimed for the system of records are reviewed
                                                                                                                                    <PT-06(02)_ODP frequency> to ensure that they have been promulgated as
                                                                                                                                    regulaons;

                                                                                                              PT-06(02)[03]         all Privacy Act exempons claimed for the system of records are reviewed
                                                                                                                                    <PT-06(02)_ODP frequency> to ensure that they are accurately described in the
                                                                                                                                    system of records noce.

